## Recommendations for follow-on tasks

1. Pre-existing dead code cleanup (SpeDocumentViewer): remove `accessToken: string` from useCheckoutFlow / useDocumentPreview options + types.ts SDAP types, delete deprecated AuthService.ts. Owner: future cleanup task or rolled into 029.
2. DocumentRelationshipViewer should remove the explicit `authority: \`https://login.microsoftonline.com/${tenantId}\`` from authInit.ts (line 55) — all other PCFs intentionally omit this to let @spaarke/auth resolve tenant via resolveTenantFromXrm (per popup regression fix from 2026-05-13). Could be silent SSO regression. Owner: likely task 025 if DocRelViewer is the SPA-side equivalent, or follow-on PCF audit.
3. After task 023 ships, the full `tsc` build of Spaarke.UI.Components should succeed without `--strict false`. Verify by running `cd src/client/shared/Spaarke.UI.Components && rm -rf dist && npm run build` post-task-023.
